cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR 

This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL) sub-categories, as it focuses on generating captions for images. The use of determinantal point process (DPP) and reinforcement learning (RL) also suggests that it may fall under the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper may touch upon information retrieval (cs.IR) as it involves generating diverse sets of captions for a single image.
